videos.description: Garrison Brooks slips past Hokies' defenders and slams home an easy two-handed flush.
videos.headline: Brooks rises for 2-handed flush

videos.description: The Tar Heels' Nassir Little drives strong to the hole and finishes through contact for an and-1.
videos.headline: Little absorbs contact for and-1

videos.description: Nassir Little turns defense into offense as he comes up with a steal and throws down a nasty slam.
videos.headline: Little skies for emphatic slam

videos.description: Garrison Brooks shows off the strength as he battles for a rebound and fights through contact for an and-1 finish.
videos.headline: Brooks muscles through contact for and-1 lay-in

videos.description: Nassir Little uses a sweet ball fake to elude Hokies' defenders and drills a deep 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Little drills deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Justin Robinson lobs it high to Ahmed Hill who throws down a nice two-handed alley-oop slam.
videos.headline: Hokies' Hill throws down alley-oop slam
